flowchart TD
    A[User Question] --> B[ask]
    B --> C[deep_recall]
    C --> D[Reset Round State]
    D --> E[Detect Strategy]

    E -->|Direct First| F[Answer Directly scope direct]
    E -->|Decompose First| H[Decompose Question]

    F --> G{Direct Answer Sufficient}
    G -->|Yes| Z[Finalize Payload]
    G -->|No| H

    H --> I[Build Question Plan]
    I --> J[Solve Sub Questions]
    J --> K[Synthesize Final Answer]
    K --> Z

    Z --> Z1[Attach Tool Calls]
    Z1 --> Z2[Collect Episode Refs]
    Z2 --> Z3[Append Refs to Answer and Evidence]
    Z3 --> O[Return Result]
